## Part 2 — Enable GitHub Pages

**Step 1** — Click **"Settings"** tab inside your repository

**Step 2** — Scroll down left sidebar and click **"Pages"**

**Step 3** — Under **"Branch"** select **"main"** and click **"Save"**

**Step 4** — Wait 2 minutes then your token list URL will be:
```
https://YOUR-GITHUB-USERNAME.github.io/token-list/tokenlist.json
```

Replace `YOUR-GITHUB-USERNAME` with your actual GitHub username and send it to me — I will verify it's working correctly before we move to the next step!

---

## Part 3 — Add to MetaMask (after GitHub Pages is live)

Once your URL is working:

1. Open **app.uniswap.org** on Sepolia
2. Click any token selector
3. Click **"Manage"** → **"Lists"**
4. Paste your GitHub Pages URL
5. Click **"Add list"**

Your fake USDT logo will now show everywhere!

---

